[I] A utility to easily take screenshot in Hyprland

[T] Hyprshot is an utility to easily take screenshot in Hyprland using your
[T] mouse. It allows taking screenshots of windows, regions and monitors which
[T] are saved to a folder of your choosing and copied to your clipboard.

